ng, impersonate a celebrity, or act out a clue. Cranium has elements similar to those of Pictionary, Charades, Trivial Pursuit: Genus Edition, Celebrities, Huggermugger, Claymania, etc.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/itemrep/img/LI4w44KvZfDdRJacsftOUtvSKC0=/fit-in/246x300/pic4994220.jpg\" alt=\"Cranium Image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">4 - 16</td>\n<td align=\"right\">13</td>\n<td align=\"right\">60m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2019-10-24T21:23:12.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"markets/awesome-ruby","categoryHTML":"<h2>Code Loaders</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/fxn/zeitwerk\">Zeitwerk</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/fxn/zeitwerk\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.6k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1640,\"repo\":\"fxn/zeitwerk\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - An efficient and thread-safe Ruby code loader.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-10-24T21:12:02.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"chiraggude/awesome-laravel","categoryHTML":"<h2>Videos</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://confidentlaravel.com/\">ConfidentLaravel</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-10-24T20:14:14.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaywcjlove/awesome-mac","categoryHTML":"<h2>Communication</h2><h4>Collaboration and Team Tools</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://slack.com/downloads/ma